http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Lottery-scam-accused-Pari-Rajan-gets-bail/article14019855.ece

Lottery scam accused Pari Rajan, who created a storm in the State police force when an electronic media channel exposed his alleged nexus with many officers, was on Monday granted bail.He had been arrested by the Criminal Investigation Department (CID) on May 1, 2015. However, the case was later transferred to Central Bureau of Investigation (CBI), which took over the case in September 2015.Pari Rajan was booked for cheating and other minor offences but the CBI has failed to file a charge sheet against him till date. On this ground, the 13th Additional Chief Metropolitan Magistrate Court granted him bail. He is likely to be released on Tuesday.